# Bound the docker build context. The api image only needs source +
# package manifests; node_modules ship as a deps stage layer, dist/
# build outputs and dev artifacts have no place in the runtime image.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.cache
**/coverage

# Local env + secrets — never enter an image.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Git internals + GitHub
.git
.github

# Test outputs + playwright artifacts
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/.vitest-cache

# Docs and design assets are not needed at runtime
docs
design
**/*.md
!**/README.md

# Editor + OS noise
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
**/*.log
